quran[135]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,Ăh
  20,2,Ur ak d Nessader ara LeqwĂŽan iwakken a p$weblev
  20,3,D asmekti kan i win ippagwaden
  20,4,D tarusi s$uĂŽ Win Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan aĂąlayen
  20,5,AĂȘnin i IĂąanncen $ef usgeld
  20,6,"IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, i illan garasen, i illan seddaw tmurt"
  20,7,"Ma tĂ©aĂąvev, ihi, Neppa IĂ©ĂŽa sser, akked wayen iffren sennig es"
  20,8,"Ăebbi, ur illi ĂŽebbi siwa Neppa. IneS ismawen imxulaf"
  20,9,Ma tusa k id teqĂ»iĂź n Musa
  20,10,"Mi iwala times, inna i twacult is: \"qqimet dagi, nek wala$ times. Amar awen d awi$, segs, asafu, ne$ ad afe$, di tmes, nnhaya"
  20,11,"Mi ibbwev $uĂŽes, Ssawlen as d: \"a Musa"
  20,12,"Nek, s tidep, d Mass ik. Ekkes arkasen ik, ih, aql ak di Ăuwa, ta$zut iĂŽqan"
  20,13,"Nek Smenyafe$ k, sell ed i uweĂȘĂȘi"
  20,14,"Nek, s tidep, d Ăebbi, ur illi ĂŽebbi siwa Nek. Ihi, Ăąabed iyI, Ă©Ă©al ilmend usmekti W"
  20,15,"Imir, s tidep, a d ias. B$i$ a t Ffre$, iwakken yal yiwen a t Nkafi $ef wayen ixdem"
  20,16,"ÂŁuĂŽek a k issefĂŽe$ fellas, win ur numin ara yis, i iddan d lhawiyya s! Mulac a pnegrev"
  20,17,"D acu p tinna deg ufus ayeffus ik, a Musa"
  20,18,"Inna: \"d taĂąkwazt iw, fellas tekkaye$, syis sse$laye$ d iferrawen i lmal iw. Sseqdace$ p i wayen nniven"
  20,19,"Inna: \"veggeĂŽ ip, a Musa"
  20,20,"IveggeĂŽ ip, tu$al d azrem, ippeĂȘnunuf"
  20,21,"Inna: \"ddem ip, ur ppagwad, ad as Nerr udem is amenzu"
  20,22,"EĂ©mev afus ik, s idis ik. A d iffe$ d amellal, ur ihlik. D assekni nniven"
  20,23,"iwakken ad ak Nessken, seg issekniyen nneÂŁ imeqwĂŽaĂȘanen"
  20,24,"ĂuĂȘ ar FerĂąun. Neppa, s tidep, d aqehhaĂŽ"
  20,25,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Lli idmaren iw"
  20,26,Sehhel iyi lameĂŽ iw
  20,27,Efsi tiyersi seg iles iw
  20,28,ad fehmen awal iw
  20,29,Efk iyi amĂąiwen di twacult iw
  20,30,gma HaĂŽun
  20,31,"Ssem$weĂŽ, syis, tazmert iw"
  20,32,Zdukkel it ar lameĂŽ iw
  20,33,iwakken a K nesbuccaĂą aĂźas
  20,34,a K id nesmekti aĂźas
  20,35,"KeĂ§Ă§, s tidep, la $ d Tepwaliv"
  20,36,"Inna: \"tepwaqbel tuppra k, a Musa"
  20,37,"Ni$ NĂąateq ik, tikelt nniven"
  20,38,"mi NweĂȘĂȘa, i yimma k, ayen i NweĂȘĂȘa"
  20,39,"err it deg usenduq, veggeĂŽ it s asif. A t issers wasif deg uqeĂŽqaĂŽ, a t iddem ucengu W, u d acengu is. Fki$ ak si lmaĂȘnana W, a ppeppuĂŽebbiv zdat wallen iW"
  20,40,"Mi telĂȘa ultma k, tenna: \"ma ad awen mle$ w ara itkelfen fellas\"? Nerra k id i yimma k, ad fukken imeĂźĂźawen is, ur tĂȘezzen ara. Ten$iv amdan, Nsellek ik si le$wben. NjeĂŽĂŽeb ik s lfetnat. Tzed$ev kra iseggwasen ar at Madian. Sinna, tusiv d s lqwedĂŽa, a Musa"
  20,41,Smenyafe$ k i iman iW
  20,42,"ĂuĂȘet, keĂ§Ă§ akked gma k, s issekniyen iW, ur stehzayet $ef usmekti W"
  20,43,"ĂuĂȘet ar FerĂąun. Neppa, s tidep, d aqehhaĂŽ"
  20,44,"Mmeslayet as s wawal amelĂȘan, amar a d immekti, ne$ ad iagwad"
  20,45,"Nnan: \"a Mass nne$! Nugad ad a$ iglez, ne$ ad ijuĂŽ"
  20,46,"Inna: \"ur ppagwadet, Nek, war ccekk, yidwen, Selle$, Pwali"
  20,47,"ĂuĂȘet $uĂŽes, tinem as: \"nekwni d imazanen n Mass ik, seddu yidne$ At IsĂŽail, ur ten ppĂąaqab ara. Aql a$ nusa k id s issekniyen n Mass ik. Tifrat i wi iddan d nnhaya"
  20,48,"S tidep, neppuweĂȘĂȘa d, ar ad ippuĂąaqeb win inekĂŽen, iwexxĂŽen"
  20,49,"Inna: \"anwa T Mass nnwen, a Musa"
  20,50,"Inna: \"Mass nne$ d Win Ifkan lxelq is i yal cci, sinna, Inha"
  20,51,"Inna: \"amek tevĂŽa d isuta timezwura"
  20,52,"Inna: \"i ten IĂ©ĂŽan, d Mass iw, di Tezmamt. Mass iw ur I$ellev, ur Iteppu"
  20,53,Win i wen irran tamurt d dduĂȘ. Iga yawen degs iberdan. Issers ed aman seg igenni. Nessuffu$ ed yissen tiyugiwin n yal Ă»Ă»enf n le$ĂŽus
  20,54,"EĂ§Ă§et, ekset lmal nnwen. Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i imawlan n ddehn"
  20,55,"Segs, Nxelq ikwen; degs, a kwen Nerr; segs, a kwen id Nessuffe$, tikelt nniven"
  20,56,"Ni$ Nessken as akw issekniyen nneÂŁ inkeĂŽ, iugi"
  20,57,"Inna: \"day a$ d tusiv, s ssĂȘur ik, a Musa, ad a$ tessuff$ev seg wakal nne"
  20,58,"War ccekk, ad ak d nawi ssĂȘur i t icban. Err garane$ yidek ppaĂąud, deg umekkan iwulmen, ur t nezgal, ur t tezgalev"
  20,59,"Inna: \"ppaĂąud nnwen ass n tme$ĂŽa, a d mlilen medden, di tĂ»ebĂȘit"
  20,60,"Izzi FerĂąun, ijmaĂą ed ccbukat is, d$a iusa d"
  20,61,"Inna yasen Musa:\"a tawa$it nnwen! Ur d garet tikerkas $ef Ăebbi, a kwen Isxev s uĂąaqeb. Ni$ ad ixseĂŽ win d igren"
  20,62,"McawaĂŽen f lameĂŽ nnsen, ffren ayen mmeslayen"
  20,63,"Nnan: \"ihi, sin agi d iseĂȘĂȘaren, b$an a kwen ssuff$en seg wakal nnwen, s ssĂȘur nnsen. Ad kksen abrid nnwen amxallef"
  20,64,"JemĂąat ed ccbukat nnwen, sinna aset ed d leĂ»fuf. Ni$ ad irbeĂȘ, assa, win iufraren"
  20,65,"Nnan: \"a Musa! A pveggĂŽev keĂ§Ă§, ne$ d nekwni ara iveggĂŽen d imezwura"
  20,66,"Inna: \"xaĂźi, veggĂŽet\"! Si ssĂȘur nnsen, iwala amzun leĂȘĂȘun imraren akked tĂąakwzin nnsen"
  20,67,"Musa, deg iman is, iĂȘus i lxuf"
  20,68,"Nenna: \"ur ppagwad! KeĂ§Ă§, s tidep, sennig sen"
  20,69,"VeggeĂŽ i illan deg ufus ik ayeffus! Ad isseblaĂą ay d snulfan\". Ay d snulfan, siwa ccbukat iseĂȘĂȘaren. Anda idda useĂȘĂȘar, ur irebbeĂȘ ara"
  20,70,"ÂŁÂšlin iseĂȘĂȘaren, knan, nnan: \"numen s Mass n HaĂŽun akked Musa"
  20,71,"Inna: \"day tumnem yiS, uqbel i wen serrĂȘe$? Neppa, zi$, d ameqwĂŽan nnwen. IsĂȘefv awen ssĂȘur. War ccekk, ad awen gezme$, avaĂŽ sya, afus sya, u a kwen Ă»emmĂŽe$ af umidag n leodar n tezdayin. A ppeĂ©ĂŽem, s tidep, anwa ay d bab uĂąaqeb meqqwĂŽen, u ara idumen sennig wiyav"
  20,72,"Nnan: \"ur k nesmenyaf, d awez$i, i wayen i $ d iusan ubeggen, akw i Win i $ Ixelqen. Seyyi i k ihwan a pseyyiv. Aseyyi k, d aseyyi $ef tmeddurt n ddunit agi kan"
  20,73,"Ih, numen s Mass nne$, iwakken ad a$ IsemmeĂȘ tuccva nne$, akked wayen n ssĂȘur i tĂȘeppmev fellane$. PifxiĂŽ Ăebbi d Imezgi"
  20,74,"Ih, Loahennama i win iusan ar Mass is, d abe$wvi. Ur ipmeppat degs, ur d ippidir"
  20,75,"Win i iusan $uĂŽeS d lmumen u ixdem ayen ilhan, widak ad ilin deg imukan aĂąlayen mavi"
  20,76,"leonanat n Ăaden, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkĂŽen din. Ayagi, d akafi i win zeddigen"
  20,77,"Ni$ NweĂȘĂȘa i Musa: \"ĂŽuĂȘ, deg iv, akked imdanen iW. Egg asen abrid akiwan, di yill. Ur ppagwad a kwen in vefĂŽen, ur ppiwĂȘic"
  20,78,"FerĂąun, s iĂąsekĂŽiwen is, vefĂŽen ten. IsseblaĂą ten yill, iĂ§Ă§a ten"
  20,79,"Itlef FerĂąun agdud is, ur inhi"
  20,80,"A yAt IsĂŽail! Ni$ Nsellek ikwen seg ucangu nnwen. Nefka yawen ppaĂąud, ar loiha tayeffus n udrar. Nessers awen d lmenna, ifeĂŽĂŽuoen"
  20,81,"EĂ§Ă§et si lmakla ilhan, i s ikwen N$at. Ur zegret tilas fellas, mulac a kwen immager urrif iW. Win immuger urrif iW, ni$ igrareb"
  20,82,"U Nek, s tidep, PsemmiĂȘe$ i win isteĂŽoĂąen, iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, d$a ipwanha"
  20,83,"Acu i k i$eĂ»ben seg ugdud ik, a Musa"
  20,84,"Inna: \"zgan deffir i. ÂŁawle$ d $ureK, a Mass iw, iwakken a PĂŽaviv"
  20,85,"Inna: \"ih, ni$ NjeĂŽĂŽeb agdud ik, deffir ek. Itelf iten Usamiri"
  20,86,"Iu$al ed Musa s agdud is, s zzĂąaf d wumri. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Day ur awen Ifka ara, Mass nnwen, lemĂąahda lĂąali? Day tĂąaĂźĂźel fellawen lemĂąahda? Ne$ day teb$am a kwen immager urrif n Mass nnwen? Tzeglem ppaĂąud iw"
  20,87,"Nnan: \"ur nezgil ppaĂąud ik, s leb$i nne$. Maca, nbubb tiĂąakkwmin n ĂŽĂŽĂȘuĂȘ n ugdud, d$a nveggeĂŽ iten. Akken i iveggeĂŽ Usamiri"
  20,88,"Issuffe$ asen d aĂąejmi, d ameslux isrugmuten. Nnan: \"wagi d ĂŽebbi nnwen u d ĂŽebbi n Musa. Ippu"
  20,89,"Day ur walan ara, ur asen d ippara awal, ur izmir a ten ivuĂŽĂŽ, ne$ a ten infaĂą"
  20,90,"Ni$ HaĂŽun inna yasen, uqbel: \"a yagdud iw! Teppuhewwlem kan, yis. Mass nnwen, s tidep, d AĂȘnin. Ddut yidi, vefĂŽet lameĂŽ iw"
  20,91,"Nnan: \"ur tnepfukku akaber is, d awez$i, alamma iu$al ed Musa $uĂŽne"
  20,92,"Inna: \"a HaĂŽun! D acu i k iĂźĂźfen, mi ten twalav nnetlafen"
  20,93,Day ur teddiv ara yidi? Day tugiv lameĂŽ iw
  20,94,"Inna: \"a mmi s n yimma! Ur iyi ppaĂźĂźaf si tamart iw, ne$ seg uqeĂŽĂŽu w. Nek, s tideps, ugade$ ad iyi d tiniv: tessemfaĂŽaqev At IsĂŽail, ur tu$ev awal iw"
  20,95,"Inna: \"d acu t leqsed ik a Usamiri"
  20,96,"Inna: \"wala$ ayen ur walan. Ddme$ d tummeĂ©t n lateĂŽ umazan, veggĂŽe$ p. Akka ay ĂȘusse$ deg iman iw"
  20,97,"Inna: \"ĂŽuĂȘ ihi, a ppevĂŽu yidek di tmeddurt a ppeqqaĂŽev: ur iyi pnalet! U, s tidep, $uĂŽek ppaĂąud ik ur tezmirev a t tzeglev. Muqel ĂŽebbi ik, u$uĂŽ mazal teqqimev, ard a t nesseĂŽ$, a t ssebruzzaĂą ar yill, wakali"
  20,98,"Mass nnwen, siwa Ăebbi. Ur illi ĂŽebbi siwa Neppa. Tamusni S tjemmel yal cci"
  20,99,"Akka i k NĂȘekku, seg isallen n zik. Ni$ Nefka yak d, s$uĂŽneÂŁ, asmekti"
  20,100,"Win i s iwexxĂŽen, ad iĂąabbi taĂąkkwemt, ass n tnekra"
  20,101,"Ad wekkĂŽen dinna. Ay dir ip fellasen ppaĂąbga, ass n tnekra"
  20,102,"Ass ideg ara d Ă»uven di lbuq, a d Nefser ibe$wviyen, zgezwen assen"
  20,103,"Ad swecwicen wa i wa: \"mraw kan i teqqimem"
  20,104,"Nekwni, Nif akw akken Nessen, ayen d qqaĂŽen, mi sen inna yiwen umxallef degsen: \"teqqimem kan ibwass"
  20,105,"Steqsayen k $ef idurar. Ini: \"a ten IssebruzzaĂą Mass iw, d iwzan"
  20,106,A ten Irr d aza$aĂŽ ibuĂŽen
  20,107,"Ur tepwaliv degs i iĂąawjen, ne$ i izzren"
  20,108,"Assen, ad vefĂŽen aberraĂȘ, war zzrug. Ad irs Ă»Ă»ut zdat UĂȘnin, a ppeslev kan i uswecwec"
  20,109,"Assen, ur ten tenfaĂą ccafuĂąa, siwa i win Iooa UĂȘnin, u IĂŽuva t $ef wawal"
  20,110,"Issen i illan zdat sen, i illan deffir sen. Ur illi sanda ara T issinen"
  20,111,Ad ĂźĂźinzen wudmawen i Umuddir n lebda. Ara ixesĂŽen d win ibubben ddens
  20,112,"Win ixeddmen ayen ilhan, u neppa iumen, ur ippagwad ddens, ne$ aqhaĂŽ"
  20,113,"Akka, Nessers it id, d LeqwĂŽan s taĂąĂŽabt. Nenewwel ed, degs, aĂąeggen, amar ad ĂȘezben, u a ten id ias usmekti"
  20,114,"D AmeqwĂŽan Ăebbi, Agellid, Tidep. Ur pĂȘiri, di t$uĂŽi, uqbel ma ifukk uweĂȘĂȘi s, $uĂŽek. Ini: \"a Mass iw! Ernu yi di tmusni"
  20,115,"Ni$ NĂąahed, zik, Adem. Ippu, ur Nufi $uĂŽes laĂązem"
  20,116,"Mi Nenna i lmalayek: \"knumt i Adem\", knant, siwa Iblis i iugin"
  20,117,"Nenna: \"a Adem, wagi, s tidep, d acengu k, akked tmeĂźĂźut ik. ÂŁurwat a kwen id issuffe$, si Loennet, a p$weblem"
  20,118,"Ih, keĂ§Ă§, degs, ur teplaĂ©ev, ur tĂąarruv"
  20,119,"S tidep, keĂ§Ă§, degs, ur tepfadev, ur k iĂźĂźuĂŽĂŽu yiĂźij"
  20,120,"I$wa t CciĂźan, inna: \"a Adem, ad ak ssekne$ ttejĂŽa uwekkeĂŽ, akw n tgelda n lebda"
  20,121,"EĂ§Ă§an segs, d$a walan iman nnsen Ăąaryan, bdan la tessĂŽen iman nnsen, s iferrawen n Loennet. Adem iaĂąĂ»a Mass is, idda di le$wlav"
  20,122,"Sinna, Ifren it Mass is, Issuref as, Inha t"
  20,123,"Inna: \"Ă»Ă»ubet segs akw, wa d acengu n wa. Ma tusa kwen id nnhaya, s$uĂŽI, win iddan d nnhaya iW, ur ipputellef, ur i$webbel"
  20,124,"Win iooan asmekti W, tameddurt is d tucmip. Ass n tnekra, a t Nefser d ader$al"
  20,125,"A d yini: \"a Mass iw! Acimi iyi Tfesrev d ader$al, ni$ lli$ pwali"
  20,126,"A d Yini: \"akken i k id iusan ssekniyen nneÂŁ, teppuv iten, akken ara tepwappuv, assa"
  20,127,"Akka ay NepqeĂźĂźi win izegren tilas, ur numin s issekniyen n Mass is. U, s tidep, aĂąaqeb n laxeĂŽt iwĂąaĂŽ kteĂŽ, u ad idum kteĂŽ"
  20,128,"Day ur ten inha ara wacĂȘal isuta i Nesqucc, uqbel nnsen? La leĂȘĂȘun $ef tnezdu$in nnsen. Deg wayagi, s tidep, d issekniyen i imawlan n ddehn"
  20,129,"Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal, s$uĂŽ Mass ik, akked lajel ipwassnen, yili, war ccekk, iĂ»aĂŽ uĂąaqeb"
  20,130,"Ihi, bibb ayen d qqaĂŽen, sbuccaĂą s ccekĂŽan Mass ik, uqbel ad inqeĂŽ yiĂźij, uqbel ad i$li, deg iv. Anez di levĂŽuf n wass, amar fellak aĂŽavi"
  20,131,"Ur ppara allen ik ar wayen i Nefka i kra n twaculin nnsen. D ajeooig n tmeddurt di ddunit, iwakken a ten NjeĂŽĂŽeb yis. A$iti n Mass ik yif it, u ad idum kteĂŽ"
  20,132,"AmeĂŽ taĂ©allit i twacult ik, ĂȘerz ip. Ur ak Nessutur ĂŽĂŽeĂ©q, d Nekwni ara k IĂŽeĂ©qen. LaĂąquba d aĂȘezzeb"
  20,133,"Nnan: \"a lemmer i $ d iusi s ussekni s$uĂŽ Mass is\"! Day ur ten id iusa ara ubeggen, deg wayen illan di tewĂŽeqtin timezwura"
  20,134,"Lemmer iten Nesqucc s uqeĂźĂźi, uqbel neppa, a d inin, war ccekk: \"a Mass nne$! Acimi ur a$ d Tunzev ara amazan? A neddu d issekniyen iK, uqbel a nendell u a neppuqeĂźĂźi"
  20,135,"Ini: \"akw, la nepgani. Ihi gganit. A ppissinem anwi i iddan d ubrid ilhan, anwi i ipwanhan"